Class LauncherCmd

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.kent.dover.fastGraph.LauncherCmd

  • public class LauncherCmd
extends java.lang.Object
    Runs the Command Line interface. This will make callbacks to Launcher to execute methods in other parts of the system This Launcher uses Apache's CLI interface to easily handle parameters and arguments. A full list of commands is available by running the software with the -h or --help parameters.
